&lt;div class="hwp-text-block field field--name-field-hwp-body field--type-text-long field--label-hidden">&lt;h3>	 &lt;/h3>&lt;h3> &lt;strong>Hardware:&lt;/strong>&lt;/h3>&lt;p>	I am happy to announce that I have finished the deployment of a variety of new workstations in our labs.  These new workstations join our Optiplex 7090s from 2021 and the super-powered Mac Pro from 2019.&lt;/p>&lt;p>	The stations include the Dell Optiplex 7000, Apple Mac Studio Max and Ultra, the Dell Precision 7865 (coming soon) You can find more information about our new workstations on our &lt;a href="https://lenwiz.github.io/hugoclone-iqss/computer-labs/lab-workstation-specifications">workstations page.&lt;/a>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Summer Staffing</title><link>https://lenwiz.github.io/hugoclone-iqss/news/news_holiday_schedules/</link><pubDate>Tue, 26 May 2026 13:38:37 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://lenwiz.github.io/hugoclone-iqss/news/news_holiday_schedules/</guid><description>&lt;main aria-label="Summer Staffing" aria-labelledby="page-title" id="main-content" lang="en" role="main" tabindex="-1">
