&lt;div class="layout-content">
&lt;div>
&lt;div class="hidden" data-drupal-messages-fallback="">&lt;/div>
&lt;article class="hwp-news-details" lang="en">
&lt;div class="hwp-news-image">
&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="hwp-news-header hwp-bg-light-base hwp-news-details" lang="en">
&lt;div class="hwp-page-title hwp-bg-light-base">
&lt;div class="hwp-container hwp-container-px hwp-py-32">
&lt;h1 class="text-large">
&lt;span>A focus on flourishing: Newest IQSS program combines social science, philosophy to understand the factors that lead to a good life&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="hwp-news--top hwp-pb-0">
&lt;div class="hwp-gap-16 hwp-flex hwp-flex-col">
&lt;div class="hwp-text-16">
&lt;div class="field field--name-field-hwp-publish-date field--type-datetime field--label-hidden">&lt;time datetime="2018-10-05T12:00:00Z">October 05, 2018&lt;/time>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="hwp-news-header__description">
&lt;div class="hwp-mx-auto">
&lt;div class="hwp-text-block field field--name-field-hwp-body field--type-text-long field--label-hidden">&lt;h5>	By Peter Reuell, Harvard Staff Writer&lt;/h5>&lt;p>	Ask most scientists about the factors that contribute to public health, and chances are you’ll hear plenty about topics like quitting smoking, eating a healthy diet and exercise, but one item that probably won’t come up is going to church. &lt;/p></description></item><item><title>The art of the online interface</title><link>https://lenwiz.github.io/hugoclone-iqss/news/news_2026_02_art_online_interface/</link><pubDate>Tue, 26 May 2026 13:37:07 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://lenwiz.github.io/hugoclone-iqss/news/news_2026_02_art_online_interface/</guid><description>&lt;main aria-label="The art of the online interface" aria-labelledby="page-title" id="main-content" lang="en" role="main" tabindex="-1">
&lt;div class="layout-content">
&lt;div>
&lt;div class="hidden" data-drupal-messages-fallback="">&lt;/div>
&lt;article class="hwp-news-details" lang="en">
&lt;div class="hwp-news-image">
&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="hwp-news-header hwp-bg-light-base hwp-news-details" lang="en">
&lt;div class="hwp-page-title hwp-bg-light-base">
&lt;div class="hwp-container hwp-container-px hwp-py-32">
&lt;h1 class="text-large">
&lt;span>The art of the online interface&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="hwp-news--top hwp-pb-64">
&lt;div class="hwp-gap-16 hwp-flex hwp-flex-col">
&lt;div class="lg:hwp-text-24">
&lt;div class="hwp-text-block field field--name-field-hwp-article-lede field--type-text-long field--label-hidden">&lt;p>&lt;span>&lt;strong>New desktop application streamlines connection between IQSS’s Dataverse and Sid&lt;/strong>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="hwp-text-16">
&lt;div class="field field--name-field-hwp-publish-date field--type-datetime field--label-hidden">&lt;time datetime="2026-02-02T12:00:00Z">February 02, 2026&lt;/time>
